casebody.data:
Thursday, May 7, 1992

MOTION DOCKET

91-2498. State v. Taylor.

Cuyahoga County, No. 59009. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution set for May 8, 1992, by the Cuyahoga County Court of Common Pleas, pending final disposition by this court,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said motion for stay be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective May 6, 1992.
